    maKhachHang ID #REQUIRED>

<!ELEMENT tenKhachHang (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT diaChi (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT soDienThoai (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT email (#PCDATA)>

